urler)|Gerald McCarthy]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1971\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|2\u201317\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|2\u201312\n|[[Croke Park]]\n|[[Tony Doran]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1972\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|3\u201312\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|1\u201310\n|[[Croke Park]]\n|[[Jim Treacy]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1973\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|1\u201313\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|2\u20138\n|[[Croke Park]]\n|[[Pat Delaney (Kilkenny hurler)|Pat Delaney]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1974\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|2\u201315\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|1\u201313\n|[[Croke Park]]\n|[[Pat Henderson]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1975\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|2\u20139\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|1\u201311\n|[[Croke Park]]\n|[[Pat Delaney (Kilkenny hurler)|Pat Delaney]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1976\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|4\u20139\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|4\u20138\n|[[Croke Park]]\n|[[\u00c9amonn O'Donoghue (hurler)|\u00c9amonn O'Donoghue]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1977\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|2\u201317\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|1\u201313\n|[[Croke Park]]\n|[[Tony Doran]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1978\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|2\u201313\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|1\u201311\n|[[P\u00e1irc U\u00ed Chaoimh]]\n|[[Charlie McCarthy (hurler)|Charlie McCarthy]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1979\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|1\u201313\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|1\u20139\n|[[Semple Stadium]]\n|[[Phil 'Fan' Larkin]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1980\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|1\u20135\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|0\u20137\n|[[Croke Park]]\n|[[Joe Connolly (hurler)|Joe Connolly]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1981\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|2\u201316\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|2\u20136\n|[[Cusack Park (Ennis)|Cusack Park]]\n|[[Joe McKenna]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1982\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|3\u20138\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|2\u20139\n|[[Tullamore]]\n|[[Se\u00e1n Silke]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1983\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|0\u201310\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|1\u20135\n|[[Cavan]]\n|[[Sylvie Lynnane]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1984\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|1\u201318\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|2\u20139\n|[[Cusack Park (Ennis)|Cusack Park]]\n|[[John Fenton (hurler)|John Fenton]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1985\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|3\u20136\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|1\u201311\n|[[Semple Stadium]]\n|[[Ger Cunningham]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1986\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|3\u201311\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|0\u201311\n|[[Ballinasloe]]\n|[[Noel Lane (Galway hurler)|Noel Lane]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1987\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|2\u201314\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|1\u201314\n|[[Cusack Park (Ennis)|Cusack Park]]\n|[[Conor Hayes]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1988\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|2\u201314\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|1\u201312\n|[[Casement Park]]\n|[[Aidan Fogarty (Offaly hurler)|Aidan Fogarty]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1989\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|4\u201316\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|3\u201317\n|[[Wexford]]\n|[[Joe Cooney]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1990\n|'''No competition'''\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1991\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|1\u201313\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|0\u201312\n|[[Croke Park]]\n|[[Pete Finnerty]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1992\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|3\u201312\n|[[Ulster GAA|Ulster]]\n|1\u20138\n|[[Nowlan Park]]\n|[[Declan Carr]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|1993\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|1\u201315\n|[[Ulster GAA|Ulster]]\n|2\u20136\n|\n|[[John Power (John Locke's hurler)|John Power]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|1994\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|1\u201311\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|1\u201310