einster GAA|Leinster]]\n|1\u201323\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|0\u201317\n|[[Pearse Stadium]]\n|[[Eddie Brennan]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|2007\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|2\u201322\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|2\u201319\n|[[Croke Park]]\n|[[John Mullane]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|2008\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|1\u201315\n|[[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n|1\u201312\n|[[O'Moore Park]]\n|[[Tommy Walsh (hurler)|Tommy Walsh]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|2009\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|3\u201318\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|1\u201317\n|[[Abu Dhabi]]\n|[[J.J. Delaney]]\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|2010 \n|'''No competition'''\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|2011\n|'''No competition'''\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|[[2012 Interprovincial Hurling Championship|2012]]\n|[[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n|2\u201319\n|[[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n|1\u201315\n|[[Nowlan Park]]\n|[[Jackie Tyrell]]\n|-\n| [[2013 Inter-Provincial Hurling Championship|2013]]\n| [[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n| 1-22\n| [[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n| 0-15\n| [[Cusack Park (Ennis)]]\n| [[Brendan Maher]] \n|-\n| [[2014 Interprovincial Hurling Championship|2014]]\n| [[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n| 1-23\n| [[Connacht GAA|Connacht]]\n| 0-16\n| [[Croke Park]]\n| [[Conal Keaney]]\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|2015\n|'''No competition'''\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[2016 GAA Interprovincial Championships|2016]]\n| [[Munster GAA|Munster]]\n| 2-20\n| [[Leinster GAA|Leinster]]\n| 2-16\n| [[Semple Stadium]]\n|- style=\"background:#d0e7ff;\"\n|}\n\n\n{{Railway Cup Hurling Championships}}\n\n[[Category:Railway Cup Hurling Championship|       ]]\n[[Category:Hurling-related lists|Finals Interprovincial Hurling Championship]]\n[[Category:Lists of Gaelic games matches|Hurling, Interprovincial finals]]\n", "name_user": "Rich Farmbrough", "label": "safe", "comment": "Update date format tag and add authority control template", "url_page": "//en.wikip