hery]]\n|-\n! 1984\n| [[Raymond Conzemius]]\n| [[Athletics (sport)|Athletics]]\n| [[Jeannette Goergen]]\n| [[Archery]]\n|-\n! 1985\n| [[Claude Michely]]\n| [[Bicycle racing|Cycling]]\n| [[Dani\u00e8le Kaber]]\n| [[Athletics (sport)|Athletics]]\n|-\n! 1986\n| [[Fonsy Grethen]]\n| [[Billiards]]\n| [[Dani\u00e8le Kaber]]\n| [[Athletics (sport)|Athletics]]\n|-\n! 1987\n| [[Robby Langers]]\n| [[Football (soccer)|Football]]\n| [[Nancy Kemp-Arendt|Nancy Arendt]]\n| [[Swimming (sport)|Swimming]]\n|-\n! 1988\n| [[Marc Girardelli]]\n| [[Skiing]]\n| [[Dani\u00e8le Kaber]]\n| [[Athletics (sport)|Athletics]]\n|-\n! 1989\n| [[Marc Girardelli]]\n| [[Skiing]]\n| [[Nancy Kemp-Arendt|Nancy Arendt]]\n| [[Swimming (sport)|Swimming]]\n|-\n! 1990\n| [[Guy Hellers]]\n| [[Football (soccer)|Football]]\n| [[Marion Hammang]]\n| [[Powerlifting|Weightlifting]]\n|-\n! 1991\n| [[Marc Girardelli]]\n| [[Skiing]]\n| [[Malou Thill]]\n| [[Powerlifting|Weightlifting]]\n|-\n! 1992\n| [[Eug\u00e8ne Berger]]\n| [[Mountaineering]]\n| [[Marion Hammang]]\n| [[Powerlifting|Weightlifting]]\n|-\n! 1993\n| [[Marc Girardelli]]\n| [[Skiing]]\n| [[Anne Kremer]]\n| [[Tennis]]\n|-\n! 1994\n| [[Marc Girardelli]]\n| [[Skiing]]\n| [[Raymonde Moes]]\n| [[Karate]]\n|-\n! 1995\n| [[Guy Hellers]]\n| [[Football (soccer)|Football]]\n| [[Nancy Kemp-Arendt]]\n| [[Triathlon]]\n|-\n! 1996\n| [[Marc Girardelli]]\n| [[Skiing]]\n| [[Nancy Kemp-Arendt]]\n| [[Triathlon]]\n|-\n! 1997\n| [[Christian Poos]]\n| [[Bicycle racing|Cycling]]\n| [[Nancy Kemp-Arendt]]\n| [[Triathlon]]\n|-\n! 1998\n| [[Dan Dethier]]\n| [[Triathlon]]\n| [[Anne Kremer]]\n| [[Tennis]]\n|-\n! 1999\n| [[Jeff Strasser]]\n| [[Football (soccer)|Football]]\n| [[Anne Kremer]]\n| [[Tennis]]\n|-\n! 2000\n| [[Kim Kirchen]]\n| [[Bicycle racing|Cycling]]\n| [[Nancy Kemp-Arendt]]\n| [[Triathlon]]\n|-\n! 2001\n| [[Jeff Strasser]]\n| [[Football (soccer)|Football]]\n| [[Ni Xia Lian]]\n| [[Table tennis]]\n|-\n! 2002\n| [[David Fiegen]]\n| [[Athletics (sport)|Athletics]]\n| [[Tessy 